menu "Status LED Configuration"

    config WOL_STATUS_LED
        bool "Enable Status LED Feedback"
        default y
        help
            Enable visual feedback via an LED for device states.
            - Fast Blink: Captive Portal Active
            - Slow Pulse: Connecting to WiFi/MQTT
            - Solid: Connected and Ready
            - Rapid Flash: Wake-on-LAN Magic Packet Dispatched

    config WOL_STATUS_LED_PIN
        int "Status LED GPIO Pin"
        default 2
        depends on WOL_STATUS_LED
        help
            The GPIO pin connected to the status LED.
            On many ESP32 dev boards, this is GPIO 2.

endmenu
